{"tid":1491051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普教中殺到埋身, 但係無乜討論咁","createTime":"2019-08-20T09:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:42:33.000Z","uid":167260,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"647213f7c362202414694ec7a9e0129ed7772f95","tid":1491051,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:33:35.000Z","msg":"已經每日150個走落嚟, 周圍都見唔少幼蝗<br />\n香港人真係會慢慢被溝淡, 但都要守住個文化, 唔可以比佢慢慢消滅咗廣東話<br />\n的確依家已經好多戰線, 但唔好忽略咗普教中既禍害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送中未完 林鄭已經搞緊全面普教中<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474241</a><br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a>"},{"pid":"54c9a527bc6526e026f6feb0c2f93ddf3ed002f4","tid":1491051,"uid":102491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔好講推 將所有核彈列明黎推post<br />\n歡迎增加任用<br />\n<br />\n置頂 曱甴論+動用私刑+日日講大話！<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 無啦啦拘捕個女人<br />\n5. 室內開槍<br />\n6. 過份使用武力+催淚彈<br />\n7. 冇委任證<br />\n8. 過期催淚彈<br />\n9. 警黑勾結<br />\n10. 無差別濫捕<br />\n11. 光明正大講大話<br />\n12. 誣蔑市民+陷害市民<br />\n13. 拆證物<br />\n14. 無視任何法律及指引<br />\n15. 葉虎事件<br />\n16. 因應政見決定做野同起訴速度<br />\n<br />\n佢地搞到香港咁樣 人人都生意差冇工開佢地仲計ot幾萬蚊準時出糧一定唔驚，諗計斷班撚樣既飯碗<br />\n香港人唔再需要唔保護市民既警察！！唔想再出糧俾一啲開槍打我 用棍扑我既人 清算黑警<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求"},{"pid":"6af2d2b7ab2cf7bdc9215b6419ee83db3666eed6","tid":1491051,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"清算黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢陰啲陰啲就過咗普教中呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e943ca9e5be3d6656b56d793e7bca6d123707e","tid":1491051,"uid":247422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"呢個要推<br />\n唔想第日仔女返黎用普通話同我溝通"},{"pid":"daf775c0e96ad990d2df7a77f378d30e2cfd0ec4","tid":1491051,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"用下其他嘢推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日係元朗721一個月啦<br />\n一個人都未檢控呀<br />\n大家記得聽日去靜坐<br />\n你地係咪想輸<br />\n從此警黑治港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpDsauC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpDsauC.jpg&h=6850f609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RV2pcHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRV2pcHY.jpg&h=29775fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520ig9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520ig9E.jpg&h=f28afdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JycD1Bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJycD1Bm.jpg&h=feb74ca6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"895519c610fa0429bd8abb25c639a66c22b36ff9","tid":1491051,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"推！救救下一代"},{"pid":"68643fa945fbf005200b8f159719be8ea14681ed","tid":1491051,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895519c610fa0429bd8abb25c639a66c22b36ff9","tid":1491051,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"推！救救下一代"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:06:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e0298d667bea7b1b386c97daafac2e1629b73","tid":1491051,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68643fa945fbf005200b8f159719be8ea14681ed","tid":1491051,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"895519c610fa0429bd8abb25c639a66c22b36ff9","tid":